## üü¢ Fully-Worked Example ‚Äî Two Engine Hypotheses

> **Quote**  
> ‚ÄúSurface anything waiting for my sign-off first, and keep overdue trainings visible until I finish them.‚Äù

| # | Theme                | Metric |
|---|----------------------|--------|
| 1 | Decision urgency     | Decision-click-rate |
| 2 | Training nudges      | Training completion |

### Hypothesis 1  
‚ÄúIf artefacts tagged `ALERT_LEVEL: CRITICAL` (approval verb + @mention + deadline < 48 h) are pinned atop their topic, Decision-click-rate will rise ‚â• 10 pp.‚Äù

**Mapping**  
*Signals* `has_approval_keyword`, `@mentioned_exec`, `deadline_hours`  
*Logic* tier rule CRITICAL first  
*UX* red üö® badge in Critical shelf  
*Safeguard* max 3 critical cards

**Metric Gate** click-rate 42 % ‚Üí **‚â• 52 %**

### Hypothesis 2  
‚ÄúIf overdue trainings re-surface every Monday, completion rises 15 pp in 30 days.‚Äù

*Signals* `training_due_flag`, `due_date`  
*Logic* weekly cron adds `ALERT_LEVEL: TRAINING_DUE`  
*UX* yellow üìö badge in Updates shelf  
*Metric* completion 60 % ‚Üí **75 %**

**14-Day Tasks (shared)**  
1. Extract signals‚ÄÉ2 d  
2. Tag + tier rules‚ÄÉ2 d  
3. FE badges‚ÄÉ3 d  
4. Flags + A/B‚ÄÉ1 d  
5. Dashboard tiles‚ÄÉ1 d  

